description:
Discover the versatility and capability of the 2022 Ford Explorer XLT. This dynamic SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience with its impressive performance, thoughtful design, and advanced technology.

• One Owner
• FRONT & SECOND ROW FLOOR LINERS (16A)

Under the hood, the 2.3L EcoBoost I-4 engine paired with a 10-Speed Automatic transmission and 4WD delivers a thrilling yet efficient ride. With 20 city/27 highway MPG, you'll enjoy the perfect balance of power and fuel economy.

The Explorer XLT's spacious and well-appointed interior offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Indulge in the comfort of the Unique Cloth Captain's Chairs, with the added luxury of Heated Front Seats. Stay connected with the SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System, complete with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration.

Versatility is at the heart of the Explorer XLT. The Split Folding Rear Seat and Power Liftgate make it easy to accommodate your ever-changing needs, whether it's hauling cargo or transporting passengers. The Four Wheel Independent Suspension and Speed-Sensing Steering ensure a smooth and responsive ride, no matter the terrain.

Experience the peace of mind that comes with the Explorer XLT's comprehensive suite of safety features. From the Dual Front Impact Airbags and Knee Airbag to the Electronic Stability Control and Rear View Camera, this SUV is designed to keep you and your loved ones secure.

Discover the perfect balance of power, technology, and utility in the 2022 Ford Explorer XLT. With its impressive capabilities and refined design, this SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience. Visit us today to take this remarkable vehicle for a test drive and see how it can enhance your life on the road.

The Avenir's premium cabin is thoughtfully designed to provide exceptional comfort and convenience. The Buick Infotainment System with built-in navigation and wireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto integration keeps you seamlessly connected on the go.

Safety and driver assistance features abound, including a Heads-Up Display, Rear Park Assist, and an enhanced Avenir design for the headlamps. The Enclave's spacious interior and flexible seating configurations make it an ideal choice for families or those with active lifestyles.

This exceptional 2023 Buick Enclave Avenir is an opportunity to own a truly remarkable vehicle. We invite you to experience its unparalleled combination of style, technology, and capability. Schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of driving this exceptional Enclave.

description:
Experience the pinnacle of versatility and sophistication with this stunning 2019 Toyota Highlander Limited. Boasting a sleek white exterior and a meticulously designed interior, this SUV is the perfect blend of power, technology, and comfort.

• Tow Hitch Receiver & Wiring Harness Package
• Special Color
• Rear Bumper Protector (TMS)

Beneath the hood, you'll find a powerful 3.5L V6 engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivering a smooth and responsive driving experience. With the added confidence of All-Wheel Drive, you can tackle any terrain with ease.

Slip into the luxurious leather-trimmed seats and be enveloped in a world of premium features. The Entune Premium JBL Audio system with Navigation and App Suite keeps you connected and entertained, while the dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone rides in comfort. The power moonroof and power liftgate add a touch of elegance and convenience to your daily drives.

Safety is paramount, and this Highlander Limited is equipped with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From the Blind Spot Monitor with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert to the Automatic High Beam Headlights, you can navigate the roads with confidence.

Whether you're embarking on a family adventure or tackling your daily commute, this 2019 Toyota Highlander Limited is the perfect companion. With its spacious interior, versatile cargo capacity, and impressive fuel efficiency, it's the ultimate SUV for those who demand the best.

Experience the exceptional craftsmanship and unparalleled capabilities of this Highlander Limited. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this SUV is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

description:
The 2023 Chevrolet Equinox LT is a versatile and well-equipped SUV that offers exceptional value and performance. With its sleek gray exterior, this Equinox is not only stylish but also highly capable, thanks to its advanced 1.5L DOHC engine and all-wheel-drive system.

This Equinox LT comes packed with an impressive array of features, including:

• CARFAX 1-Owner
• CONFIDENCE & CONVENIENCE PACKAGE
• Driver Confidence II Package
• Driver Convenience Package
• Wireless Apple CarPlay/Wireless Android Auto
• Heated Driver & Front Passenger Seats
• 2-Way Power Driver Lumbar Control Seat Adjuster
• Driver 8-Way Power Seat Adjuster
• 17" Aluminum Wheels
• Rear Power Liftgate
• Heated Door Mirrors
• Lane Change Alert w/Side Blind Zone Alert

Beyond these standout features, the Equinox LT offers a host of additional amenities that enhance both the driving experience and your overall comfort. Dual-zone automatic climate control, a premium audio system, and a suite of advanced safety technologies work together to create a truly exceptional vehicle.

With an EPA-estimated 24 city/30 highway MPG, this Equinox LT delivers impressive fuel efficiency, allowing you to go further on every tank. Its spacious and versatile interior provides ample room for passengers and cargo, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

At our dealership, we're committed to providing our customers with exceptional service and a hassle-free buying experience. We understand that purchasing a vehicle is a significant investment, and we're here to ensure that you find the perfect Equinox LT to meet your needs.

We invite you to come in and experience the 2023 Chevrolet Equinox LT for yourself. Let our knowledgeable sales team guide you through the features and capabilities of this impressive SUV, and see how it can enhance your driving experience. With a list price of $22,361, this Equinox LT represents an outstanding value in the competitive SUV market.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this Equinox LT your own. Visit our showroom today and let us help you take the first step towards owning this exceptional vehicle.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of efficiency and sophistication in this 2017 Ford Fusion Hybrid SE. With its sleek white exterior and impressive hybrid powertrain, this Fusion is poised to exceed your expectations and redefine your daily driving experience.

Packed with a wealth of premium features, this Fusion SE Hybrid offers unparalleled value. Key highlights include:

• Upgraded Sideview Mirrors with Heat, Auto-Dimming, and Integrated Turn Signals
• Intelligent Access with Remote Start System
• Heated Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel
• LED Headlamps, Fog Lamps, and Taillamps
• SYNC 3 Communications and Entertainment System with 8-inch Touchscreen
• Power Converter 110V Outlet
• Blind Spot Information System (BLIS) with Cross-Traffic Alert
• Lane-Keeping System with Lane-Keeping Alert and Aid
• Pre-Collision Assist with Pedestrian Detection

Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional fuel efficiency of this Fusion Hybrid. Boasting an EPA-estimated 43 mpg in the city and 41 mpg on the highway, this vehicle will help you save at the pump while reducing your carbon footprint. The advanced hybrid powertrain seamlessly blends the power of a gasoline engine with the efficiency of an electric motor, delivering a responsive and smooth driving dynamics.

Comfort and convenience are paramount in this well-appointed Fusion. The Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel and Heated Front Bucket Seats provide a luxurious touch, while the Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control and Rear Window Defroster ensure a comfortable cabin environment year-round. The SYNC 3 system with 8-inch Touchscreen, Android Auto, and Apple CarPlay integration keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

Prioritize safety with the comprehensive suite of driver-assist technologies, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Pre-Collision Assist with Pedestrian Detection, Blind Spot Monitoring, and Lane-Keeping System. These advanced features work together to help you navigate the road with confidence and peace of mind.

This 2017 Ford Fusion Hybrid SE is a testament to Ford's commitment to innovation and excellence. Experience the perfect blend of efficiency, technology, and sophistication by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident this Fusion will exceed your expectations and become your trusted companion on the road.

AutoNation USA Ft Myers is honored to present a wonderful example of pure vehicle design... this 2016 Mazda CX-5 Grand Touring only has 56,261mi on it and could potentially be the vehicle of your dreams! If you're in the market for an incredible SUV -- and value on-the-road comfort and manners more than ultimate off-road prowess or tow capacity -- you'll definitely want to check out this Mazda CX-5 Grand Touring. When it comes to high fuel economy, plenty of versatility and a great looks, this MazdaCX-5 Grand Touring cannot be beat. This Mazda CX-5's superior fuel-efficiency is proof that not all vehicles are created equal. A Mazda with as few miles as this one is a rare find. This CX-5 Grand Touring was gently driven and it shows. You'll see the world in a whole new way thanks to the navigation system that comes with this vehicle. Added comfort with contemporary style is the leather interior to heighten the quality and craftsmanship for the Mazda CX-5 Grand Touring. More information about the 2016 Mazda CX-5: The 2016 Mazda CX-5 competes with the likes of the Honda CR-V, Subaru Forester, Toyota RAV4 and Ford Escape. Even in this crowd, it's one of the sportiest-driving models, with surprisingly good fuel economy ratings considering that. The Mazda CX-5 also stands out for offering a great ride quality and a flexible, spacious interior. The Mazda CX-5's infotainment system, with Bose sound, is one of the most feature-packed in its competitive set, too, with things like well-integrated Pandora internet radio. Strengths of this model include good set of safety features, full-features audio and infotainment, Perhaps the best-handling in its class, excellent fuel economy ratings, stylish exterior, and perky powertrain (Touring and Grand Touring)

Discover the exceptional 2023 GMC Yukon SLT, a remarkable SUV that seamlessly blends power, comfort, and advanced technology. This stunning vehicle is the perfect companion for your adventures, offering a dynamic driving experience and a wealth of premium features to elevate your everyday commute.

• 3.0L I-6 Diesel Turbocharged (Duramax) (277 hp [206.6 kW] @ 3750 rpm, 460 lb-ft of torque [623.7 N-m] @ 1500 rpm)
• SEATS, SECOND ROW BUCKET, MANUAL-FOLDING
• ENGINE BLOCK HEATER

Slip behind the wheel and experience the refined elegance of the Yukon SLT. With its striking White exterior and sleek, modern design, this SUV commands attention wherever it goes. The 10-speed automatic transmission with Overdrive and Rear-Wheel Drive deliver a smooth, responsive ride, while the 3.0L I6 engine provides the power you need for effortless acceleration and confident handling.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin that caters to your every need. The Perforated Leather-Appointed Seating, Heated and Ventilated Driver and Front Passenger Seats, and 2nd Row Manual-Folding Bucket Seats ensure unparalleled comfort and convenience. The Bose 9-Speaker Stereo Audio System and SiriusXM with 360L keep you entertained, while the Navigation System and Wireless Charging provide seamless connectivity.

Safety is paramount in the Yukon SLT, with features like Forward Collision Alert, Lane Keep Assist with Lane Departure Warning, and Automatic Emergency Braking working tirelessly to protect you and your loved ones. The Rear Cross Traffic Alert and Front & Rear Park Assist further enhance your driving confidence, making maneuvering in tight spaces a breeze.

Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional 2023 GMC Yukon SLT. This SUV is the perfect blend of power, style, and technology, offering a truly remarkable ownership experience. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can transform your daily drives and weekend adventures.

Call us at 512-900-7062

We search the country for the very best inventory and hand-select each vehicle we offer for sale. Contact a SweetCars representative now to park this Audi S7 in your garage today!

description:
The 2023 Toyota GR Corolla Morizo Edition in Wind Chill Pearl with a Cockpit Red interior is a rare, track-focused hot hatch developed to the personal specifications of Toyota president and Gazoo Racing Master Driver Akio “Morizo” Toyoda. Limited to just 200 numbered units for the 2023 model year, this highly collectible GR Corolla delivers extreme performance, lightweight construction, and motorsport-inspired engineering in a street-legal package. Engine & Performance
• 1.6L turbocharged G16E-GTS 3-cylinder DOHC engine
• 300 hp and 295 lb-ft of torque
• 6-speed intelligent manual transmission with rev-matching (iMT)
• GR-FOUR all-wheel drive with selectable torque splits
• Front and rear limited-slip differentials Exterior Features
• Wind Chill Pearl exterior finish
• 18" forged alloy wheels in matte black
• LED projector headlights with auto high-beams
• Front fog lamps and LED brake lights
• Sport lip spoiler and black grille Interior & Comfort
• Brin-Naub and synthetic leather sport seats with red accents
• Cockpit Red interior with red stitching and red seat belts
• Sport simulated suede steering wheel and shifter
• Voice-activated automatic air conditioning
• Tilt/telescoping steering column Technology & Safety
• Toyota Audio Multimedia with 8" touchscreen
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility
• Back-up camera and Dynamic Radar Cruise Control
• Integrated navigation with real-time traffic
• Front and side airbags with perimeter alarm Additional Details
• Sport-tuned suspension
• Mechanical limited-slip differential
• Tire mobility kit
• Proximity key with push-button start
• Limited-production Morizo Edition (200 units)

description:
Experience the thrill of owning this meticulously maintained one-owner 2023 Audi S5 Sportback, a masterpiece of German engineering that blends blistering performance with luxurious refinement in a stunning Ibis White exterior that gleams under any light, paired with a sophisticated black interior ready to envelop you in comfort and style.
Unleash the raw power of its 3.0-liter TFSI V6 engine, roaring to life through an 8-speed Tiptronic transmission and the legendary quattro all-wheel drive system that grips the road like nothing else, delivering heart-pounding acceleration and razor-sharp handling whether you're carving through twisty backroads or cruising effortlessly on the highway. Dive into a world of cutting-edge technology with the Premium Plus Package, where auto-dimming power-folding exterior mirrors with memory adjust seamlessly to your preferences, an advanced alarm system with motion sensor keeps watch, and the immersive Bang & Olufsen sound system with 3D audio transforms every drive into a concert hall experience, complete with SiriusXM featuring 360L for endless entertainment.
Stay connected and in command with Audi MMI Navigation plus guiding your journeys, driver's seat memory ensuring perfect positioning every time, rear USB charging ports for passengers, parking system plus combined with a top view camera system for effortless maneuvering in tight spots, and luxurious leatherette coverings on the center console and door armrests adding a touch of elegance. Safety and convenience soar with Audi side assist including pre sense rear to alert you of hidden dangers, adaptive cruise control with Traffic Jam assist that handles stop-and-go traffic with ease, Audi active lane assist keeping you centered, Audi phone box for wireless charging, and a heated steering wheel with hands-on detection that warms your grip on chilly mornings. Elevate your experience further with the Navigation Package, bringing Audi connect PLUS for smart connectivity, enhanced MMI Navigation plus, and the breathtaking Audi Virtual Cockpit Plus that displays vital information in a fully digital, customizable dashboard. As you approach, the Audi beam S beam projects a striking "S" logo, announcing your arrival with flair, while inside, heated front seats, three-zone automatic climate control with digital display, and power-adjustable front seats with lumbar support cradle you in supreme comfort. With advanced features like anti-lock braking protection, electronic vehicle immobilization, tire pressure monitoring, and Audi pre sense basic for proactive occupant protection, this S5 Sportback not only thrills but protects with top-tier safety, earning impressive government ratings including five stars in rollover resistance.
This one-owner gem also boasts a carbon atlas inlay for a sporty interior accent, diamond-stitched S sport seats with power side bolsters and massage function for ultimate support during spirited drives, and a garage door opener integrated into the HomeLink system for seamless home access, making every moment behind the wheel an adrenaline-fueled adventure wrapped in unparalleled luxury and innovation.

description:
This Ford Blue Advantage Blue Certified 2023 Honda Civic Type R Touring delivers track-bred performance, everyday usability, and legendary Honda engineering in a rare, enthusiast-grade hot hatch. With just 32,224 miles, this Civic Type R stands out as one of the most desirable performance cars on the road, offering a true driver’s experience for enthusiasts throughout Wesley Chapel, Tampa, Brandon, Clearwater, and the greater Tampa Bay area.

Finished in Boost Blue Pearl with a Black and Red interior, this Type R makes a bold statement with its aggressive widebody design, functional aero elements, and unmistakable motorsport presence. The 19-inch matte black wheels wrapped in ultra-high-performance summer tires, LED lighting, sculpted rocker extensions, and the signature triple-center exhaust reinforce that this is not an ordinary Civic — it is engineered for serious driving.

Under the hood is Honda’s turbocharged 2.0L VTEC engine paired with a 6-speed manual transmission and a helical limited-slip differential. This powertrain delivers razor-sharp throttle response, thrilling acceleration, and remarkable control through corners. Adaptive suspension with multiple drive modes allows the car to transform from daily commuter to track weapon at the push of a button, while Brembo brakes provide exceptional stopping power.

Inside, the Touring cabin blends performance with comfort. High-bolstered sport seats trimmed in suede-effect fabric, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, aluminum pedals, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a fully digital driver display create a cockpit that is focused, immersive, and refined. The Bose premium audio system, wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, built-in navigation, and wireless charging keep the car practical for everyday life.

Safety and driver-assist features include Blind Spot Information System, Collision Mitigation Braking System, Forward Collision Warning, Cross Traffic Monitor, adaptive cruise control, lane keeping assist, and a full complement of airbags, delivering confidence without compromising performance. :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}

As a Ford Blue Advantage Blue Certified vehicle, this Civic Type R includes a 90-day/4,000-mile Comprehensive Limited Warranty, 24/7 Roadside Assistance, and a CARFAX Vehicle History Report, providing added peace of mind after delivery.

This Civic Type R may also qualify for Parks Plus benefits, which can include protective coatings for paint, headlights, and interior surfaces, anti-theft VIN etching, on demand roadside assistance, ID theft protection and restoration, $2,500 stolen vehicle assistance and collision loyalty credit, cabin sanitizer with antimicrobial protectant, and Nationwide Lifetime Warranty coverage, adding long-term ownership value.

If you are searching for one of the most capable front-wheel-drive performance cars ever built, this Blue Certified 2023 Honda Civic Type R Touring is a rare opportunity in the Tampa Bay market.

description: Experience executive-level luxury, breathtaking design, and advanced innovation in this *2023 Audi A7 Prestige*, a premium sportback that seamlessly blends performance, technology, and refined sophistication. With its sleek fastback silhouette and unmistakable Audi presence, the A7 delivers a driving experience that feels both powerful and elegantly composed.Turbocharged performance provides smooth, confident acceleration and refined power delivery for effortless city driving and highway cruising. Audi engineering emphasizes precision and balance, while legendary quattro all-wheel drive enhances traction and stability in a wide range of road and weather conditions. The result is a composed, athletic ride that feels engaging without sacrificing comfort.Inside, the cabin reflects Audi's highest standards of craftsmanship and modern design. The Prestige trim surrounds you with premium materials, refined finishes, and advanced features that elevate every drive. Audi Virtual Cockpit Plus delivers crisp, customizable digital displays, while the dual-touchscreen MMI infotainment system, smartphone integration, and available navigation keep you seamlessly connected and informed. The spacious interior offers generous passenger comfort, while the sportback design provides versatile cargo access without compromising the A7's elegant profile.Advanced safety and driver assistance technologies are thoughtfully integrated to support confidence and peace of mind. These intelligent systems are designed to enhance awareness, assist with everyday driving tasks, and help provide reassurance in traffic and on longer journeys.Striking, innovative, and unmistakably Audi, the 2023 Audi A7 Prestige is an exceptional choice for drivers seeking luxury, performance, and cutting-edge technology in a refined sportback that stands apart from the ordinary.Visit Audi Owings Mills, 9804 Reisterstown Road, Owings Mills, MD 21117 today!

Celebrated for its motorsport DNA and driver-focused design, the Civic Type R delivers an exhilarating experience that turns every road into an event.A high-output turbocharged engine delivers thrilling acceleration and immediate response, while a performance-tuned suspension and precision steering provide razor-sharp handling and exceptional control. Designed to inspire confidence at speed, the Civic Type R feels planted through corners and composed on the highway, offering a driving experience that's as engaging as it is rewarding.Inside, the Touring trim elevates the performance-focused cockpit with premium touches and advanced technology. Supportive sport seating, a driver-centric layout, and intuitive controls keep you connected to the road, while modern infotainment and digital displays enhance convenience without distracting from the drive. Performance instrumentation and thoughtful details reinforce the Civic Type R's race-bred character.Despite its track-ready capability, the Civic Type R remains practical for daily use, offering usable passenger space and cargo flexibility that make it easy to enjoy every day. Its bold design and unmistakable presence ensure it stands out wherever it goes, while Honda's reputation for reliability adds confidence to ownership.Honda of Serramonte offers convenient sales and service of both new Honda cars along with high quality and in-demand pre-owned cars, trucks and SUVs. We have a wide range of vehicles to suit your needs and our experienced sales staff is ready to assist you! We are located at 485 Serramonte Blvd, Colma, CA 94014. Come by and visit our showroom or call us at (888) 892-5461 -- hondaofserramonte.com.

Born from motorsports DNA, the GR Corolla delivers an intense, driver-focused experience that transforms every road into your personal playground.At the heart of this performance machine is a turbocharged engine tuned for explosive response and exhilarating acceleration, paired with a performance-focused drivetrain that delivers exceptional grip and control. The result is razor-sharp handling, confident cornering, and a visceral connection to the road that makes every drive unforgettable. Whether carving through back roads or powering down the highway, the GR Corolla Premium is built to excite.Inside, the cabin reflects its performance mission with a sporty, driver-centric layout and premium touches throughout. Supportive sport seating, purposeful design elements, and advanced technology create an environment that keeps you engaged and in command. Modern infotainment, digital displays, and driver-assistance features add convenience and confidence without dulling the raw excitement this vehicle is known for.Despite its track-inspired performance, the GR Corolla remains practical for everyday life. Its compact hatchback design offers flexibility for passengers and cargo, making it easy to balance performance driving with daily responsibilities. This is a rare combination of practicality and performance that few vehicles can match.If you're looking for a bold, high-energy driving experience wrapped in a distinctive performance package, the 2025 Toyota GR Corolla Premium delivers excitement at every turn.At Audi Central Houston, it's not just our offices, customer lounges and parts and service facilities that are high tech. Equally forward-thinking is the professional, informative and friendly way we do business. With our client-centric approach, we pride ourselves in providing drivers with an entirely new way to shop for, maintain, and embrace the Audi luxury-performance tradition. This 2025 MINI Hardtop 2 Door Cooper S, has a Blazing Blue Metallic exterior and an Grey/Blue interior color. 3,925 miles. Stock Number SS12751. No Accidents! One Owner! Important Package and Feature Information Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. Experience the perfect blend of athletic design, advanced technology, and everyday versatility in the 2025 Audi A5 Sportback. The Audi Sound System, garage door transmitter (HomeLink), and steering wheel mounted audio controls make every journey intuitive and enjoyable. Visibility and safety are enhanced with auto high beam headlights, delay off headlamps, rain sensing wipers, and a clear rear-view camera.

Exterior refinement meets practicality with features such as power heated mirrors with turn signal indicators, a power liftgate, and a sleek power moonroof that brightens the cabin. Remote keyless entry and speed sensitive wipers add convenience to your daily routine.

Indulge in the convenience of Bluetooth/Hands-Free Cell Phone, the expansive Moonroof/Sunroof, and the added security of the Rear Backup Camera. Navigate with ease using the integrated Navigation system, and enjoy the seamless connectivity of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The Leather upholstery and Audi Advanced Key provide a touch of elegance, while the Go Luxury Black Out Package adds a bold, exclusive flair.

• Bluetooth/Hands-Free Cell Phone
• Moonroof/Sunroof
• Rear Backup Camera
• Navigation
• Leather
• One Owner
• Remainder of Factory Warranty
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Non Smoker
• Go Luxury Black Out Package

Beneath the sleek exterior, this A5 Sportback is powered by a potent 2.0L 4-Cylinder TFSI engine paired with a responsive 7-Speed Automatic S tronic transmission and quattro all-wheel drive. With an impressive 23 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway, you'll enjoy exceptional efficiency and performance.

Elevate your driving experience with the Audi Virtual Cockpit Plus, which provides a customizable digital instrument cluster, and the Audi Side Assist with Pre Sense Rear, which enhances your awareness and safety on the road. The Heated Front Sport Seats and Heated Steering Wheel will keep you comfortable, while the Power Liftgate and Split Folding Rear Seat offer unparalleled versatility.

This A5 Sportback also boasts a wealth of advanced safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, Overhead Airbag, and Occupant Sensing Airbag. The Emergency Communication System and Exterior Parking Camera Rear provide added peace of mind.

With an original MSRP of $51,940, this 2025 Audi A5 Sportback 45 S line Premium quattro is now available for just $32,495. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the ultimate in luxury, performance, and technology. Schedule a test drive today and discover the exceptional value this vehicle has to offer.

description:
Discover the perfect balance of efficiency, style, and technology in the 2025 Toyota Prius XLE. This exceptional hybrid vehicle is a true testament to Toyota's commitment to innovation and sustainability.

Boasting an impressive array of features, the Prius XLE is designed to elevate your driving experience. Key highlights include:

• Remote keyless entry
• Traction control
• ABS brakes
• Low tire pressure warning
• Electronic Stability Control
• Heated door mirrors
• Illuminated entry
• Alloy wheels

The Prius XLE's 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT engine and Continuously Variable (ECVT) AWD powertrain deliver exceptional fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 49 mpg in the city and 50 mpg on the highway. This means you can enjoy the open road with confidence, knowing you're reducing your environmental impact and saving on fuel costs.

As a Toyota Gold Certified pre-owned vehicle, this Prius XLE has undergone a rigorous 160-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty package. You can drive with peace of mind, knowing that your investment is protected by:

• 12-month/12,000-mile Limited Comprehensive Warranty
• 84-month/100,000-mile Powertrain Limited Warranty
• 7-year/100,000-mile Roadside Assistance
• $0 deductible

With its striking "Cutting Edge" exterior color and a wealth of advanced features, the 2025 Toyota Prius XLE is the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency.   • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.

With only *6,401 miles*, this Prius Prime offers near-new condition and outstanding value for drivers seeking advanced plug-in hybrid technology backed by Toyota reliability. Powered by a responsive 2.0L 4-cylinder plug-in hybrid system, it provides smooth, quiet performance with the flexibility of EV and hybrid driving modes, making it ideal for daily commuting and longer trips.The interior and exterior design flow together seamlessly, featuring a modern driver-focused cabin with comfortable fabric seating, a digital gauge cluster, intuitive touchscreen infotainment with smartphone integration, fade-to-off interior lighting, and smart storage throughout. The hatchback layout adds everyday practicality while maintaining the Prius Prime's clean, aerodynamic profile.Efficiency is a major highlight, with impressive electric driving capability for short trips and excellent hybrid fuel economy when operating in hybrid mode, making this Prius Prime an excellent choice for drivers looking to reduce fuel costs without sacrificing convenience.Safety and driver-assistance technologies include Toyota Safety Sense 3.0 with Pre-Collision System, Lane Tracing Assist, Blind Spot Monitoring with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, Driver Monitoring Alert, a backup camera, multiple airbags, and tire pressure monitoring, all designed to support confidence and peace of mind on every drive.On the outside, the Prius Prime showcases a sleek, futuristic appearance with LED lighting, sharp body lines, and a streamlined silhouette that emphasizes efficiency and modern Toyota design. The Wind Chill Pearl exterior adds a crisp, upscale finish that stands out while remaining easy to maintain.If you're looking for a low-mileage plug-in hybrid that blends advanced technology, outstanding efficiency, and modern style, this 2025 Toyota Prius Prime SE is an excellent choice. Visit us today to experience it for yourself.*Earnhardt Toyota**6136 E Auto Loop Ave, Mesa, AZ 85206**480-807-9700*

Performance & Driving Experience The 2025 Toyota Prius Plug-In Hybrid SE delivers an impressive blend of efficiency, innovation, and everyday drivability. Its plug-in hybrid powertrain allows for electric-only driving on short trips while maintaining excellent fuel economy for longer journeys, making it an ideal choice for drivers seeking lower fuel costs without compromising versatility. The vehicle provides a smooth, composed ride with confident handling, supported by advanced driver-assistance features that enhance safety and awareness in daily driving situations. A complimentary CARFAX vehicle history report is included, giving you full transparency into prior ownership and maintenance history. Toyota Certified benefits include:
  • Powertrain Limited Warranty: Get 84 months or 100,000 miles of coverage (whichever comes first) from the date of purchase, ensuring your vehicle stays protected for years.
  • Limited Comprehensive Warranty: Enjoy 12 months or 12,000 miles of coverage (whichever comes first) starting from the date of purchase.
  • $ Warranty Deductible: Benefit from zero deductible on covered repairs, saving you money.
  • 160-Point Inspection: Each Toyota Certified Used Vehicle (TCUV) undergoes a rigorous 160-point quality check to ensure it meets Toyota's high standards.
  • Transferable Warranty: Increase your vehicle’s resale value with a warranty that transfers to the next owner at no extra cost.
  • 7-Year/100,000-Mile Roadside Assistance: Drive worry-free with roadside assistance available 24/7 for up to 7 years or 100,000 miles.
  • New-Car Financing Rates: Take advantage of standard new-car financing rates available through Toyota Financial Services, making your purchase more affordable.
  • Nationwide Warranty Acceptance: Enjoy the confidence of warranty coverage honored at over 1,400 Toyota dealers across the U.S. and Canada.
  • Reconditioning by Experts: TCUVs are reconditioned to Toyota’s standards by dealer-trained technicians, ensuring top-notch quality.
  • High Resale Value: Toyota vehicles are renowned for their reliability and durability, contributing to excellent resale value.
  • Free CARFAX Vehicle History Report: Know your vehicle’s past with a complimentary CARFAX report, providing added peace of mind.
  • Smooth Transaction Handling: We manage all aspects of your purchase, including DMV paperwork, making the buying process easy and stress-free.
  • Easy Trade-Ins: We accept trade-ins to help you upgrade your vehicle seamlessly.
Why Buy from Titan Motor Group At Titan Motor Group, we focus on transparency, quality, and a seamless buying experience. Every Certified vehicle is thoroughly reconditioned by Toyota-trained technicians and competitively priced to deliver long-term value and confidence. If you’re looking for a nearly new plug-in hybrid with advanced safety features, outstanding efficiency, and Toyota Certified protection, this 2025 Toyota Prius Plug-In Hybrid SE is an excellent choice. This 2025 MINI Hardtop 4 Door Cooper S, has a Midnight Black II Metallic exterior and Beige interior color with only 5,983 miles. Stock Number 918677. You can connect with us by calling (775) 337-9649. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2025 Volkswagen Golf GTI 2.0T SE. This meticulously maintained vehicle boasts a captivating Blue exterior, complemented by a well-appointed interior that exudes sophistication and style.

Packed with an impressive array of features, this Golf GTI is a true performance-oriented masterpiece. Key highlights include:

• Navigation System
• 9 Speakers
• harman/kardon® Speakers
• Air Conditioning
• Power Driver Seat
• Power Moonroof: Panoramic
• Forward Collision: FCW w/Autonomous Emergency Braking Mitigation
• Auto High-Beam Headlights
• Heated Front Top Sport Seats
• Heated Steering Wheel
• ArtVelours Seating Surfaces
• Alloy Wheels: 18" 2-Tone Diamond-Turned

Powered by a robust 2.0L TSI DOHC engine, this Golf GTI delivers an exhilarating driving experience, with a 7-Speed DSG Automatic transmission and FWD providing exceptional responsiveness and control. Boasting an impressive 24 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway, this vehicle offers the perfect balance of performance and efficiency.

Beyond its impressive capabilities, the Golf GTI also showcases a wealth of advanced technology and convenience features. The MIB3 Discover Pro AM/FM/HD With 12.9" Touchscreen Navigation system provides seamless connectivity and intuitive infotainment, while the VW Car-Net Safe & Secure 5-year emergency communication system offers added peace of mind.

Comfort and style are equally impressive, with heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and the premium ArtVelours seating surfaces providing a truly luxurious driving experience. The panoramic moonroof and 18" alloy wheels further enhance the vehicle's stunning aesthetics, ensuring you'll turn heads wherever you go.

With its exceptional performance, advanced technology, and refined interior, this 2025 Volkswagen Golf GTI 2.0T SE is a true standout in the compact performance segment. We invite you to experience its remarkable capabilities firsthand. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover the joy of owning this exceptional vehicle.

description:
Why BUY from MINI of Fairfield County? When you choose this Icy Sunshine Blue Metallic 2025 MINI Hardtop 4 Door Cooper S with 5,312 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! One Owner! What this vehicle includes: GREY/BLUE, VESCIN/CLOTH UPHOLSTERY Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
Come on in to MINI of Fairfield County today at 154 Post Rd. Darien CT 06820 or call 203-348-4700 to schedule a test drive!

Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, the MINI John Cooper Works Iconic exudes a bold, distinctive style that is sure to turn heads. This exceptional 2025 MINI John Cooper Works Iconic is now available for $36,800. Experience the thrill of driving and the joy of ownership by scheduling a test drive at our showroom today. We're confident that once you take this MINI for a spin, you'll be captivated by its unparalleled performance, cutting-edge technology, and uncompromising style.

description: Unlock the thrill of pure performance with the 2025 Toyota GR Corolla Premium. This exceptional vehicle is a true driver's delight, combining uncompromising power, refined handling, and a host of premium features that will elevate your driving experience.Boasting a remarkable 300 horsepower from its turbocharged 1.6L I3 engine, the GR Corolla Premium delivers exhilarating acceleration and responsive control. Paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive, this car is engineered to conquer the road with confidence. Standout features include:LIFETIME WARRANTY!One Owner! Clean CarFax!BACKUP CAMERALOCAL TRADE-INNON SMOKER300 HPNavigation system: Drive Connect Cloud Navigation (1-year trial subscription)Radio: Toyota Audio Multimedia w/8 JBL SpeakersBrin Naub & Synthetic Leather Seat TrimThe GR Corolla Premium's striking exterior in sleek Black commands attention, while the interior boasts premium touches like heated sport front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a leather-wrapped shift knob. With a city fuel economy of 19 MPG and 27 MPG on the highway, this performance-focused Toyota offers an exceptional balance of power and efficiency.Beneath the surface, the GR Corolla Premium is engineered to deliver a thrilling driving experience. Its four-wheel independent suspension, speed-sensing steering, and electronic stability control provide precise handling and responsive feedback, allowing you to carve through corners with ease. The 4-wheel disc brakes with ABS ensure confident stopping power, while the rear spoiler and bold design cues accentuate the car's sporty persona.Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front and side impact airbags, a rear-view camera, and an emergency communication system providing added peace of mind. The GR Corolla Premium is a true testament to Toyota's commitment to engineering excellence, blending breathtaking performance with a wealth of premium amenities.Experience the pinnacle of Toyota's performance heritage. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate the unparalleled capabilities of the 2025 Toyota GR Corolla Premium. This exceptional vehicle is waiting to unleash its power and transform your driving experience.

description:
The 2026 Toyota Prius XLE is a mid-level trim of the latest Prius hybrid hatchback that blends Toyotas improved fifth-generation hybrid powertrain with enhanced comfort and tech features. Powered by a 2.0-liter gasoline engine paired with an electric motor, the XLE delivers around 194 hp (FWD) or 196 hp (AWD) and strong fuel economy - approximately 52 MPG combined for front-drive models and about 49 MPG combined for all-wheel drive versions - making it an efficient choice for daily commuting and longer trips. As a hybrid, it incorporates Toyotas proven hybrid system with a continuously variable transmission and hatchback versatility with seating for five and a practical cargo area.

Compared with the base Prius LE, the XLE adds a number of comfort and convenience upgrades that give it a more upscale feel. Standard equipment includes 19-inch alloy wheels, heated front seats and steering wheel, synthetic leather (SofTex) upholstery, an auto-dimming rearview mirror, wireless smartphone charging, and parking sensors with low-speed automatic braking - with available options like a larger 12.3-inch touchscreen, panoramic glass roof, and digital key capability. It also comes with a suite of advanced driver-assistance features as part of Toyota Safety Sense 3.0, helping balance efficiency with a modern, well-equipped driving experience.

description:
This 2021 Volkswagen Golf 1.4T TSI with 52,101 miles proves that practical doesn’t have to be boring. Compact, quick on its feet, and quietly refined, this Golf is the kind of car that makes every drive feel easy while still keeping things fun behind the wheel.

The turbocharged 1.4T engine delivers smooth, responsive power that’s perfect for city driving and surprisingly confident on the highway. Its balanced handling and tight footprint make parking lots and traffic a breeze, while the overall ride stays comfortable and composed no matter where you’re headed.

Inside, the black leather interior gives the cabin a clean, upscale feel. Heated front seats add comfort on cold mornings, Apple CarPlay keeps your apps and music seamlessly connected, and Blind Spot Monitoring adds an extra layer of confidence on busy roads. The moonroof brings in fresh air and light, making this compact hatch feel more open and inviting than you’d expect.

This Golf has passed Archibald’s Certified inspection process, meaning it’s been thoroughly checked, fully reconditioned inside and out, and backed by a 3-month or 3,000-mile limited warranty for added peace of mind. description: . Stylish and comfortable, our 2021 Toyota Corolla XSE Sedan in Super White brings a bolder approach to compact cars! Powered by a 2.0 Liter Dynamic Force 4 Cylinder that serves up 169hp connected to a Dynamic-Shift CVT with traditional first gear for quick off-the-line acceleration. Our Front Wheel Drive sedan also shows off sharp handling and rewards you with nearly 38mpg on the highway, and its striking design boasts LED lighting, a power sunroof, and the sporty flair of prominent rocker panels set off by a rear spoiler and 18-inch alloy wheels. The XSE interior features an athletic look with SofTex® heated front seats, eight-way power for the driver, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and an uplevel instrument panel. For your convenience, automatic climate control and a Smart Key system are matched with advanced technology that includes an 8-inch touchscreen, app-based full-color navigation, an Entune Audio Plus sound system, and impressive connectivity thanks to WiFi compatibility to go with Amazon Alexa compatibility, Apple CarPlay®, Android Auto®, and Bluetooth®. Toyota provides you with an incredible level of protection as well, thanks to a backup camera and its Safety Sense technology that includes a pre-collision system, lane-departure alert, pedestrian detection, and dynamic radar cruise control. With all that and more, our Corolla is a blast to drive and easy to own! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership! .   • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.

Trusted Name for 60+ Years Serving our community for over six decades with integrity, quality, & customer satisfaction The Hansel Auto Group story begins in 1851. Joseph Hansel first entered the transportation industry selling horse-drawn carriages. Joseph's son continued to build the Hansel name, opening the family's first automotive dealership in 1901. Hansel Auto Group first expanded into the Sonoma Valley in 1961 under the leadership of Walter Hansel. Walter believed that the Hansel name was about more than just selling cars. We are committed to giving back to our community. Walter Hansel partnered with multiple other local business owners to found what would become the local chapter of United Way. This began a long tradition of community involvement by the Hansel family.

description:
Introducing the 2021 Toyota Corolla Hatchback SE Nightshade Edition - a captivating blend of style, technology, and performance that's sure to elevate your driving experience. With its sleek white exterior and a host of premium features, this Corolla Hatchback is the perfect companion for the modern, discerning driver.

Standout features include:

• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Bluetooth/Hands-free Cell Phone
• Rear View Camera
• Push Button Start
• Lane Keep Assist
• Adaptive Cruise Control
• All-Weather Floor Liners (TMS)

Beyond the impressive technology, this Corolla Hatchback also boasts a spirited 2.0L I4 engine, delivering an exceptional 32 city/41 highway MPG. The CVT transmission and front-wheel drive ensure a smooth, efficient ride, while the sporty handling and independent suspension provide a truly engaging driving experience.

But the real beauty of this Corolla Hatchback lies in its versatility. The spacious interior, with its split-folding rear seats, offers ample room for passengers and cargo alike. Whether you're commuting to the office, embarking on a weekend getaway, or simply running errands around town, this Corolla Hatchback is up for the task.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, knee airbags, and electronic stability control ensuring your peace of mind behind the wheel. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear and Auto High-beam Headlights add an extra layer of confidence and convenience.

But don't just take our word for it. Come experience the 2021 Toyota Corolla Hatchback SE Nightshade Edition for yourself. We're confident that once you get behind the wheel, you'll be captivated by its dynamic performance, cutting-edge technology, and uncompromising style. Visit our showroom today and let us help you discover the perfect Corolla Hatchback to suit your lifestyle.

Why BUY from Bill Jacobs Volkswagen? When you choose this Mythos Black Metallic 2021 Audi A5 Sportback S line Premium Plus with 27,264 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: Convenience Package
  • Audi Side Assist with Pre Sense Rear
  • Alarm System with Motion Sensors
  • Driver Seat Memory
  • Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirrors
  • Heated Steering Wheel
  • Audi Advanced Key
  • Parking System Plus (front/rear Acoustic Sensors)
  • SiriusXM All Access Service
Premium Plus ($4,900 value)
  • Adaptive Cruise Control with Traffic Jam Assist
  • Audi Active Lane Assist
  • Hands-On Detection Steering Wheel
  • Power Folding Exterior Mirrors
  • Matrix-Design LED Headlights
  • Top View Camera System
  • 2 Rear USB Charge Ports
  • Convenience Package
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Audi smartphone interface with Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
Come on in to Bill Jacobs Volkswagen today at 2211 Aurora Ave Naperville IL 60540 or call 844-746-7928 to schedule a test drive!

INFO ABOUT THIS VEHICLE: Our Wind Chill Pearl 2021 Toyota Prius Prime XLE has 25,051 miles with Black interior color has been certified and is ready for you! Stock Number WU30215 Important Package Information Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Certification benefits include:

  • Reconditioning by Experts: TCUVs are reconditioned to Toyota’s standards by dealer-trained technicians, ensuring top-notch quality.
  • High Resale Value: Toyota vehicles are renowned for their reliability and durability, contributing to excellent resale value.
  • Free CARFAX Vehicle History Report: Know your vehicle’s past with a complimentary CARFAX report, providing added peace of mind.
  • Smooth Transaction Handling: We manage all aspects of your purchase, including DMV paperwork, making the buying process easy and stress-free.
  • Easy Trade-Ins: We accept trade-ins to help you upgrade your vehicle seamlessly.
Toyota certification ensures reliability, protection, and long-term ownership confidence.   • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • With this system the driver's hands must remain on the wheel at all times but can be removed briefly (for a few seconds), otherwise the vehicle will prompt the driver to put their hands back on the wheel.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.
  • Mobile devices can wirelessly connect to the internet through the vehicle's private mobile network.
Fair Market Pricing We use advanced technology, real-time market data, and third-party tools like KBB, Edmunds and Carfax to ensure our prices are competitive. This market-driven approach guarantees transparency and gives you confidence in every purchase. Fast & Easy Buying Process Upfront pricing saves time, keeping the focus on finding the perfect car. Haggle-Free Price Clear, upfront pricing, ensuring transparency & trust in every deal. The price you see is the price you pay. *30 Day/1,000 Mile Limited Warranty *Applies to used cars 12 model years or newer & under 100,000 Miles. Excludes select electric & H-value vehicles that are AS IS cars. Please see dealer for additional information. A copy of the warranty is available for review the dealership. Trusted Name for 60+ Years Serving our community for over six decades with integrity, quality, & customer satisfaction The Hansel Auto Group story begins in 1851. Joseph Hansel first entered the transportation industry selling horse-drawn carriages. Joseph's son continued to build the Hansel name, opening the family's first automotive dealership in 1901. Hansel Auto Group first expanded into the Sonoma Valley in 1961 under the leadership of Walter Hansel. Walter believed that the Hansel name was about more than just selling cars. We are committed to giving back to our community. Walter Hansel partnered with multiple other local business owners to found what would become the local chapter of United Way. This began a long tradition of community involvement by the Hansel family.

description: CLEAN TITLE*Sunburst Auto Sales Center is proud to present the sophisticated 2021 Audi A5 Sportback in a sleek PREMIUM trim with a glossy black finish that exudes elegance and class. The LED Daytime Running Lights (DRL) and semiautomatic headlamp beam switching ensure you're visible and can see the road ahead in any condition. Whether you're commuting to work or embarking on a weekend getaway, this Audi A5 Sportback is the epitome of luxury and safety. Visit Sunburst Auto Sales Center today and experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence.

CARFAX One-Owner. Experience efficient, all-electric driving with premium comfort in this 2021 Nissan LEAF SL Plus, finished in Brilliant Silver Metallic with a refined Black leather-appointed interior. As Nissans longest-running electric vehicle, the LEAF continues to deliver impressive range, advanced technology, and everyday practicality in a compact, easy-to-drive package.

Powered by a high-output electric motor paired with a single-speed reducer, the LEAF SL Plus provides smooth, instant acceleration and quiet operation. With an outstanding 114/94 City/Highway MPGe, this EV is ideal for commuters and eco-conscious drivers looking to reduce fuel costs without sacrificing comfort or features.

The SL Plus trim brings upscale amenities throughout the cabin, including leather-appointed seating, heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, power driver seat, automatic climate control, and HomeLink garage door transmitter. The spacious hatchback design offers excellent cargo flexibility for daily errands or weekend trips.

Technology highlights include NissanConnect EV with Navigation & Services, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, a Bose premium audio system, and a crisp infotainment display designed to keep you connected on every drive. Safety and driver-assist features include rear parking sensors, electronic stability control, automatic high-beam headlights, and multiple advanced airbag systems.

This LEAF rides on 17-inch alloy wheels and includes thoughtful details such as kick plates, splash guards, and carpeted floor and cargo mats, making it a well-rounded and highly efficient electric hatchback.

The Napleton Auto Group promotes a no pressure buying experience that puts the customer in charge of the buying process, and for over 80 years, the Napleton family has made sure that absolutely nothing is more important than our commitment to your satisfaction. Our staff members are professional in every sense of the word, and receive regular training, including factory certification, so they are truly knowledgeable about the vehicles we offer. We want every customer's experience to be as timely, comfortable and ultimately as satisfying as it possible can be. You'll see it in every department of every Napleton Auto Group dealership. We hope you'll join the thousands of other satisfied customers that buy and service their vehicles the Napleton way. One Owner! This 2021 Toyota Prius LE AWD-e offered in Supersonic Red will make a great addition to your family or business! Be sure to take note of all this vehicle has to offer: Special Color ($425 value)
    Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
    Other notable features: SUPERSONIC RED, MOONSTONE, FABRIC SEAT TRIM Napleton Downtown Chevrolet Buick GMC is proud to serve customers in communities throughout the Chicagoland area. Give us a call at 312-588-9421 or stop by to test drive your new car, truck, or SUV today! 2720 S. Two owner and clean Carfax: this 2024 Honda Civic Sport Touring presents in excellent condition after careful ownership and routine maintenance. Well maintained history and a clean vehicle report make this Civic a dependable choice for buyers seeking a high quality compact sedan with premium features and modern styling.

Performance and efficiency: The Sport Touring combines a responsive turbocharged engine with a refined continuously variable transmission to deliver spirited acceleration, confident highway passing, and competitive fuel economy. Sport tuned suspension and precise steering provide engaging handling for city driving and long trips alike.

Exterior and design: Sport Touring trim enhances the Civic with sport inspired body accents, sleek LED headlights and taillights, premium alloy wheels, and a bold front grille that elevates visual appeal. Aerodynamic styling improves efficiency while projecting a contemporary presence on the road.

Interior and comfort: A premium cabin features leather trimmed seating, heated front seats, ambient interior lighting, and a driver focused cockpit with ample legroom and cargo capacity. Thoughtful storage, comfortable rear seating, and a versatile trunk make daily errands and weekend travel convenient.

Technology and connectivity: The Sport Touring includes an advanced touchscreen infotainment system with wireless Apple CarPlay and wireless Android Auto, integrated navigation, premium audio, Bluetooth hands free calling, and multiple USB ports to keep devices synced and charged. Clear driver displays and intuitive controls reduce distraction and enhance usability.

Safety and driver assistance: Honda Sensing safety suite provides adaptive cruise control, lane keeping assist, collision mitigation braking system, road departure mitigation, and traffic sign recognition to offer layered protection and increase driver confidence.

Condition and value: Two owner history and a clean Carfax report combined with meticulous servicing make this 2024 Honda Civic Sport Touring an attractive option for buyers seeking a sporty, tech loaded, and reliable compact sedan. Competitive financing, certified pre owned options, and extended warranty plans may be available to suit your needs.

OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring

This 2024 Honda Civic Sport, has a Boost Blue Pearl exterior and an Black interior color. 25,263 miles. Stock Number TC682268A. You can connect with us by calling (580) 223-1500. No Accidents! OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

description:
CarFax No Accidents! CarFax One Owner! Popular Options and Features Include: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

description:
Introducing the 2023 Honda Civic Sport Touring, a sleek and sophisticated sedan that combines impressive performance with a wealth of premium features. This stunning vehicle is the epitome of modern automotive design, blending style, technology, and comfort to deliver an unparalleled driving experience.

Boasting an impressive array of features, the 2023 Civic Sport Touring is equipped with:
• Navigation system: Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System
• Bose Premium Audio System
• Rear window defroster
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Emergency communication system: HondaLink
• Power moonroof
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Auto High-beam Headlights
• Security system
• Heated door mirrors
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Garage door transmitter: HomeLink
• Outside temperature display
• Heated Front Bucket Seats
• Split folding rear seat
• 18" Alloy Wheels
• Rear window wiper

Beneath the sleek exterior, the 2023 Honda Civic Sport Touring is powered by a 1.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine, delivering an impressive 30 city/37 highway MPG. This dynamic powertrain, paired with the smooth-shifting CVT transmission and front-wheel drive, provides a thrilling and responsive driving experience that will leave you eager to take on the open road.

Step inside the 2023 Civic Sport Touring, and you'll be greeted by a meticulously crafted interior that exudes sophistication and attention to detail. The leather-trimmed seating surfaces, heated front seats, and power-adjustable driver's seat ensure unparalleled comfort, while the Bose Premium Audio System and integrated navigation system provide cutting-edge technology at your fingertips.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the 2023 Civic Sport Touring delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance features. From the Blind Spot Information (BSI) System to the Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS), you can enjoy the peace of mind that comes with knowing you and your passengers are well-protected.

As you consider your next vehicle, the 2023 Honda Civic Sport Touring should be at the top of your list. With its exceptional performance, premium features, and uncompromising safety, this sedan is the perfect blend of style, technology, and driving enjoyment. We invite you to visit our showroom and experience the 2023 Civic Sport Touring for yourself. Let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can enhance your daily commute and weekend adventures.

    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
