Discover the ultimate driving experience with this stunning 2023 Toyota Prius Limited. This exceptional hybrid vehicle combines unparalleled efficiency, advanced technology, and a sleek, modern design that will turn heads wherever you go.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Prius Limited is equipped to elevate your driving experience:

• Navigation system: Drive Connect Cloud Navigation (1-year trial subscription)
• Apple CarPlay
• Forward Collision Warning
• Lane Departure Warning
• Lane Keep Assist

Designed to keep you connected and safe, this Prius Limited is packed with cutting-edge technology that will revolutionize the way you commute. Enjoy the convenience of seamless smartphone integration with Apple CarPlay, while the advanced safety features, including Forward Collision Warning and Lane Departure Warning, provide an added layer of protection on the road.

Beneath the striking exterior lies a powertrain that delivers exceptional efficiency. Powered by a 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT engine paired with a Continuously Variable (ECVT) transmission and AWD, this Prius Limited boasts an impressive 49 MPG in the city and 50 MPG on the highway, ensuring you'll spend less time at the pump and more time exploring the open road.

The interior of this Prius Limited is equally impressive, with premium features that elevate your driving experience. Slip into the comfortable and supportive heated and ventilated sport front bucket seats, and enjoy the added convenience of a power liftgate and a Harman Kardon premium audio system.

But the true standout feature of this Prius Limited is its uncompromising commitment to sustainability. As a hybrid vehicle, it offers a greener, more eco-friendly driving experience, allowing you to reduce your carbon footprint without sacrificing performance or style.

Whether you're commuting to the office, running errands, or embarking on a road trip, this 2023 Toyota Prius Limited is the perfect companion. With its exceptional efficiency, advanced technology, and premium amenities, it's the ultimate expression of modern, sustainable driving.

Experience the future of automotive innovation and schedule a test drive today. This Prius Limited won't be on our lot for long, so don't miss your chance to make it your own.

This 2023 MINI Hardtop 2 Door Cooper S, has a Chili Red exterior and a Carbon Black interior color. Please call us at 561-529-3101 and reference stock number G9287.No Accidents! One Owner! WHY THIS VEHICLE? Important Package Information: Signature Trim
  • 7-Speed Sport DCT Transmission
  • Body Color Roof
  • Panoramic Moonroof
  • Aluminum Interior Surface
  • Touchscreen Media Display
 Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Predictive brake assist - Be prepared for your big brake. Predictive brake assist monitors the available distance in front of you compared to your vehicles speed. If your speed exceeds the required distance to stop short of a collision, it readies your brakes to apply maximum stopping force when you use them. Predictive brake assist helps see to it that you stop.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring

description:
Discover the perfect blend of efficiency and style with the 2023 Toyota Prius XLE. This exceptional hybrid vehicle offers a remarkable combination of advanced technology, premium features, and exceptional fuel economy, making it an outstanding choice for the eco-conscious driver.

Boasting an impressive list of features, the Prius XLE stands out from the crowd. Key highlights include:

• 6 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Radio data system
• Radio: Audio System
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Rear window defroster
• Power driver seat
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls

Beneath the sleek exterior, the Prius XLE is powered by a 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT engine paired with a Continuously Variable (ECVT) transmission, delivering an exceptional 49 city/50 highway MPG. This advanced powertrain not only provides outstanding fuel efficiency but also ensures a smooth and responsive driving experience, even with the added capability of All-Wheel Drive.

Step inside the Prius XLE and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring Heated Sport Front Bucket Seats, a Heated Steering Wheel, and Synthetic Leather Seat Trim for unparalleled comfort and style. The intuitive technology suite, including an Exterior Parking Camera Rear and Auto High-beam Headlights, enhances your driving experience and provides added peace of mind.

Safety is also a top priority in the Prius XLE, with features like Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control ensuring your protection on the road. The Emergency Communication System: Safety Connect further adds to your security, providing access to emergency assistance at the touch of a button.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2023 Toyota Prius XLE. This exceptional hybrid offers a winning combination of efficiency, technology, and premium amenities, making it the ideal choice for the discerning driver. Visit our showroom today to test drive this remarkable vehicle and discover the future of automotive innovation.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Head-up display - Keep your head up! You don't have to take your eyes off of the road to get information from your dashboard anymore. With head-up display, important driving information - like speed and RPM's - displays on your windshield in your line of sight. Because when you're driving, the most important information lies on the road ahead. Keep your eyes on the road with head-up display.
  • Predictive brake assist - Be prepared for your big brake. Predictive brake assist monitors the available distance in front of you compared to your vehicles speed. If your speed exceeds the required distance to stop short of a collision, it readies your brakes to apply maximum stopping force when you use them. Predictive brake assist helps see to it that you stop.

Joseph Hansel first entered the transportation industry selling horse-drawn carriages. Joseph's son continued to build the Hansel name, opening the family's first automotive dealership in 1901. Hansel Auto Group first expanded into the Sonoma Valley in 1961 under the leadership of Walter Hansel. Walter believed that the Hansel name was about more than just selling cars. We are committed to giving back to our community. Walter Hansel partnered with multiple other local business owners to found what would become the local chapter of United Way. This began a long tradition of community involvement by the Hansel family.

Introducing the **2019 Volkswagen Beetle 2.0T S**, a certified gem that offers a captivating blend of retro aesthetics and cutting-edge safety and performance features. This model is equipped with a powerful **2.0L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine**, delivering a thrilling 174 horsepower through a seamless 6-speed automatic transmission.

The Beetle is designed for those who appreciate efficiency without sacrificing excitement. Its turbocharged engine not only enhances performance but also ensures excellent fuel economy, making it perfect for both city driving and long highway journeys.

Safety is paramount, and the Beetle excels in this area with an array of advanced features. The **rear camera** provides a clear view of whats behind you, ensuring safer reversing and parking. Complementing this is the **brake assist** feature, which detects emergency braking situations and applies maximum stopping power to help prevent accidents.

For those long drives, the **cruise control** feature allows for a more relaxed driving experience. Just set your desired speed, and the Beetle will maintain it, reducing fatigue and enhancing fuel efficiency.

The user-friendly **touchscreen** interface simplifies access to entertainment and navigation, ensuring a smooth drive. Plus, with **wireless audio streaming**, you can effortlessly enjoy your favorite music or podcasts without the clutter of cords.

The **rear collision warning** system adds an extra layer of safety by monitoring the area behind you and alerting you to potential hazards, making every drive a little more secure.

Moreover, the Beetles innovative **variable valve timing** and **intercooled turbo** technology enable a more efficient engine performance, resulting in cleaner emissions and a reduced environmental impact. This means you can enjoy spirited drives while being environmentally conscious.

In summary, the **2019 Volkswagen Beetle 2.0T S** is an outstanding choice for drivers who seek an exceptional blend of style, safety, and dynamic performance. Its iconic design and modern features make it a head-turner on the road, offering a delightful driving experience. Dont miss the opportunity to own this unique modern classic! Experience the charm and innovation of the Volkswagen Beetle today!

This 2019 Volkswagen Golf GTI Rabbit Edition (rare!), has a Pure White exterior and an Titan Black w/Clark Plaid interior color. 35,912 miles. Stock Number P13943. You can connect with us by calling 888-326-2786. No Accidents! One Owner! Mint! OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

Discover this used 2019 Volkswagen Golf , a practical and fuel-efficient compact hatchback that combines everyday usability with sporty style and modern technology. Powered by a turbocharged 1.4 L four-cylinder engine producing 147 hp and 184 lb-ft of torque , this Golf delivers a balanced mix of performance and efficiency with an EPA-estimated 29 MPG city/37 MPG highway (~32 MPG combined) . Inside, youll find a well-designed cabin with intuitive infotainment including Apple CarPlay and Android Auto , Bluetooth, and a responsive touchscreen system. Comfortable seating for five and fold-flat rear seats provide flexibility for passengers and cargo alike. Safety has been enhanced with standard features such as blind-spot monitoring, autonomous emergency braking, forward-collision warning, and a backup camera all designed to help you stay confident on the road. Key Highlights: Turbocharged 1.4 L engine efficient and responsive performance (~147 hp, 184 lb-ft). Up to ~32 MPG combined fuel economy great for commuting and long drives. Smart tech features Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth. Advanced safety systems blind-spot monitoring, emergency braking, backup camera. Flexible cargo space 60/40 folding rear seats for gear and groceries. Comfortable interior with seating for five. Flexible financing options available at AutoNation Spokane Valley. Whether youre searching for an efficient daily driver or a hatchback with practical cargo space, the 2019 Volkswagen Golf delivers value, tech, and reliability in one compact package.

Discover the exceptional 2019 BMW X3 sDrive30i, a premium SUV that combines dynamic performance, sophisticated style, and unparalleled comfort. This meticulously maintained vehicle is a true testament to BMW's engineering excellence, offering a captivating driving experience that will exceed your expectations.

Boasting a striking white exterior, this X3 sDrive30i is equipped with a range of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Highlights include:

Boasting an impressive EPA-estimated 23 mpg in the city and 30 mpg on the highway, this SUV combines performance and efficiency for a truly rewarding ownership experience.

Beyond its exceptional performance, the 2019 X3 sDrive30i offers a refined and sophisticated interior, with features such as dual-zone automatic climate control, a premium sound system, and a sleek, modern design that complements the dynamic exterior. The spacious and versatile cabin provides ample room for passengers and cargo, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

As a trusted BMW dealer, we take pride in offering our customers exceptional vehicles that exemplify the brand's commitment to quality and innovation. This 2019 X3 sDrive30i is a prime example of that dedication, and we believe it could be the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

We invite you to experience the exceptional 2019 BMW X3 sDrive30i for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of owning a truly remarkable SUV. We look forward to the opportunity to assist you in finding the perfect vehicle to meet your needs and exceed your expectations.

Joseph Hansel first entered the transportation industry selling horse-drawn carriages. Joseph's son continued to build the Hansel name, opening the family's first automotive dealership in 1901. Hansel Auto Group first expanded into the Sonoma Valley in 1961 under the leadership of Walter Hansel. Walter believed that the Hansel name was about more than just selling cars. description: Discover the exceptional value and unparalleled features of this 2019 Toyota Prius XLE. With its striking white exterior and an impressive array of advanced technologies, this Prius is the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and convenience. Boasting an impressive list of premium features, this Prius XLE is designed to elevate your driving experience. Key highlights include: ? Color Head-Up Display (HUD) ? Garage Door Transmitter Powered by a robust 1.8L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V VVT-i engine, the Prius delivers an exceptional fuel economy of 54 MPG in the city and 50 MPG on the highway, making it an exceptional choice for the eco-conscious driver. The advanced Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT) provides smooth and responsive power delivery, ensuring a refined and efficient driving experience. Beyond its impressive performance, the Prius XLE offers a wealth of cutting-edge technologies to keep you connected and entertained. Enjoy the seamless integration of the Entune Audio system, complete with a CD player and steering wheel-mounted audio controls. The Rear Camera with Dynamic Gridlines provides added confidence and convenience when maneuvering in tight spaces. Safety is also a top priority in the Prius XLE, with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, Overhead Airbag, and Electronic Stability Control. These advanced systems work together to help protect you and your passengers in the event of an accident. With its sleek, modern design, exceptional fuel efficiency, and impressive list of premium features, this 2019 Toyota Prius XLE is the perfect choice for the discerning driver who demands both style and substance. We invite you to experience the exceptional value and refined driving dynamics of this remarkable vehicle. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this Prius can enhance your daily commute and elevate your driving experience.

description:
We are proud to offer this 2019 Mazda Mazda3 Hatchback w/Preferred Pkg in Machine Gray Metallic with Greige interior and offers 26 city/35 highway mpg. CarFax No Accidents! CarFax One Owner! We're a proud member of the Ken Harvey Auto Group, which means we're one of several family-owned and family-operated dealerships. We realize that our success depends upon your satisfaction and has for decades. Here at Dublin Mazda, we strive to provide our customers with welcoming, convenient and genuine experiences. From the vehicle purchasing process to servicing your Mazda, it is our mission to make you feel like family. Our goal is to have the biggest selection of Used Mazdas in Northern California. But it's all about quality, so we keep only the finest trade-ins and get rid of the rest, which means you're always picking from the best. And with Mazda booming in popularity, we get lots of non-Mazda trade-ins, too. Regardless of brand, every used car we offer comes with the Ken Harvey Advantage, your guarantee of quality. Popular Options and Features Include: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace.   • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? Safety and Security
  • Ignition immobilizer - Theft is a non-starter. You can feel more secure about your vehicle being there when you come back. Ignition immobilizer is a passive security system consisting of a transmitter in the ignition key and a sensor located in the vehicle. If both are not present or do not recognize each other, the vehicle will not start. Ignition immobilizer a sure-fire way to prevent the theft of your vehicle.

description:
I-5 Cars has been Family Owned & Operated since 2001, providing our community with quality pre-owned vehicles and exceptional customer service.

This 2011 Toyota Prius Two is a standout choice for the eco-conscious driver seeking a reliable and fuel-efficient ride. With its impressive 51 city/48 highway MPG, this Prius will help you save at the pump while reducing your carbon footprint.

• LOCAL TRADE IN
• Remote keyless entry
• Traction control
• ABS brakes
• Low tire pressure warning
• Electronic Stability Control
• Heated door mirrors
• Illuminated entry
• Alloy wheels

Under the hood, the 1.8L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT-i engine delivers a smooth and responsive performance, paired with a CVT transmission for seamless acceleration. The Prius's front-wheel-drive system provides confident handling, making it a pleasure to drive in a variety of conditions.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior, featuring a AM/FM/MP3 CD player, air conditioning with automatic temperature control, and power windows and doors for your comfort and convenience. The split-folding rear seat offers versatility, allowing you to accommodate both passengers and cargo with ease.

Safety is a top priority, and this Prius comes equipped with a suite of advanced features, including dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and an occupant sensing airbag system. You can drive with confidence, knowing you and your loved ones are well-protected.

With its striking red exterior, this Prius Two is not only environmentally friendly but also visually appealing. The alloy wheels and spoiler add a touch of sporty flair, while the heated door mirrors and illuminated entry provide added convenience.

Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or embarking on a road trip, this 2011 Toyota Prius Two is an exceptional choice that will exceed your expectations. Experience the joy of driving a fuel-efficient and well-equipped vehicle that aligns with your values.

I-5 Cars has been Family Owned & Operated since 2001, providing our community with quality pre-owned vehicles and exceptional customer service. We invite you to visit our showroom and take this Prius for a test drive. Let us help you find the perfect vehicle to meet your needs and exceed your expectations.

But the GTI Base isn't just about speed and power, it also offers a smooth and responsive ride thanks to its advanced suspension system. Plus, with its fuel-efficient engine, you can enjoy your drive without worrying about frequent stops at the gas station.

Don't miss your chance to own this 2011 Volkswagen GTI Base. With its impressive performance, stylish design, and top-notch safety features, it is the perfect choice for anyone looking for a versatile and reliable vehicle. So why wait? Come take a test drive and experience the thrill of the GTI Base for yourself!

This 2016 Toyota Prius c Four is proudly offered by AutoNation Toyota White Marsh This 2016 Toyota Prius c has great acceleration and wonderful styling without sacrificing exceptional fuel economy. The Prius c Four is well maintained and has just 98,394mi. This low amount of miles makes this vehicle incomparable to the competition. This is the one. Just what you've been looking for. More information about the 2016 Toyota Prius c: One of the most remarkable things about the Prius is how little it asks from the owner in exchange for its legendary fuel efficiency. Special fuel isn't needed, no need to plug the Prius into the wall at night, drivers are not consigned to a tiny interior and miniature storage space and finally, premium mileage numbers don't have to cost an arm and a leg. The Prius drives, handles and behaves just like any other mid-sized car. It just happens to get the kind of fuel economy that makes people do a double take. Starting at around $25,000 the Prius is competitive with other cars in its price bracket, offering ample interior space, a quiet comfortable ride, plenty of interior gadgets and world-famous mileage figures. The 2016 Ford Focus ST is a fun, performance-oriented hot hatch that combines turbocharged power with everyday practicality. Powered by a 2.0L EcoBoost turbocharged 4-cylinder engine paired with a 6-speed manual transmission and front-wheel drive, it delivers strong acceleration, sharp handling, and an engaging driving experience.

This example has a clean title and clean Carfax, reflecting careful ownership and no accident history. With low mileage for its year, it has been well maintained and remains in very good mechanical and cosmetic condition.

A short-throw shifter has been installed, providing quicker, more precise gear changes and enhancing the overall driving feel. The drivetrain feels tight and responsive, making this ST especially enjoyable to drive.

Finished in [insert exterior color] over [insert interior color], the Focus ST features sport seats, touchscreen infotainment with Bluetooth connectivity, backup camera, premium audio system, dual-zone climate control, alloy wheels, and ST-specific performance styling.

The engine runs strong, the transmission shifts smoothly, and the suspension feels composed and sporty. The interior is clean and well-kept, and the exterior shows only normal wear consistent with mileage.

Well known for its performance, reliability, and practicality, this 2016 Ford Focus ST is an excellent choice for anyone looking for a fun daily driver with true enthusiast appeal.

description:
At Lake View Ford we believe that your car buying experience should be an enjoyable one. It's our goal to exceed your expectations in every way so that each and every time your family needs a car or truck, you know exactly where to go. We set out to accomplish that by staying firmly rooted in our values of integrity and professionalism in order to provide you with a truly superior customer service experience. A proud member of the Dean Auto Group, we're sure you'll find the quality new or used vehicle you want from the manufacturers you love! Find exactly what you're looking for at a price that makes you smile... This 2016 Volkswagen Golf GTI Autobahn w/Performance Pkg has a beautiful Pure White exterior with Titan Black interior. This vehicle has 86,263 miles has been thoroughly inspected by our factory trained service technicians and has been fully reconditioned for immediate delivery. We're happy to provide this Golf GTI's CARFAX vehicle history report upon request as well. No Accidents! IMPORTANT PACKAGE INFORMATION Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.
We value-price our vehicles to assure our customers get an easy & notable car buying experience. With every New & Pre-Owned purchase you become part of our Lake View Ford family, and being a family member has benefits: 1. description:
Introducing the 2007 Toyota Prius Base - the ultimate eco-friendly and fuel-efficient vehicle on the market. With its sleek design and innovative technology, this hybrid car is sure to turn heads and save you money at the pump.

Equipped with a 1.5L 4-cylinder engine and electric motor, the Prius Base delivers an impressive 60 mpg in the city and 51 mpg on the highway. That's right, you can drive past the gas station with confidence knowing you're making a positive impact on the environment.

Step inside and experience the spacious and comfortable cabin, complete with plush cloth seats and modern features such as keyless entry and a premium sound system. The Prius Base also comes with all the essential safety features, including multiple airbags and anti-lock brakes.

But that's not all, this 2007 model also comes with extra space for all your needs. With 14.4 cubic feet of cargo space, you can easily fit all your groceries, sports equipment, or luggage for a weekend getaway.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own a 2007 Toyota Prius Base - the perfect combination of style, efficiency, and practicality. Hurry in and take a test drive today!

description:
Clean CARFAX. 2014 Toyota Prius c Model Two – Fuel-Smart, City-Ready Hybrid

This 2014 Toyota Prius c Model Two delivers legendary Toyota reliability with outstanding fuel efficiency and a compact, urban-friendly design. Finished in Black Sand Pearl with a gray cloth interior, this 5-door hatchback is perfect for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone looking to cut fuel costs without sacrificing comfort or safety.

Powered by a 1.5L 4-cylinder Atkinson-cycle hybrid engine paired with a continuously variable automatic transmission (CVT), the Prius c offers an impressive 53 MPG city/46 MPG highway. Multiple drive modes (Eco, EV, and Power) let you tailor performance to your driving style, while regenerative braking helps maximize efficiency.

Inside, the cabin is thoughtfully designed with automatic climate control, digital driver information display, Bluetooth hands-free connectivity, and steering-wheel-mounted controls. Comfortable front bucket seats, ample storage, and a versatile hatchback cargo area make this Prius c as practical as it is economical.

Safety is a top priority, featuring front, side, and curtain airbags, driver knee airbag, tire pressure monitoring, rear child safety locks, stability control, ABS, and hill-hold assist for added confidence on the road.

Additional highlights include:

Model Two Package

Projector beam headlights with daytime running lights

LED brake lights and rear spoiler

Hybrid system monitor

Carpeted floor mats and trunk mat

50-state emissions compliance

If you want exceptional fuel economy, proven hybrid technology, and a stylish compact design, this 2014 Toyota Prius c Model Two checks all the right boxes.

This 2014 Fiat 500L Easy is the perfect blend of style, technology, and versatility. Priced to move, this 2014 Ford Focus SE offers the best price in the area for buyers seeking quality and affordability in Ypsilanti, MI. Whether you're a first-time driver, a student, or anyone looking for dependable transportation, this Ford Focus delivers smart value and proven performance. Don't miss out on this competitively priced, CARFAX-verified compact that checks the boxes for safety, efficiency, and comfort. This 2014 Ford Focus features cruise control for long trips. Electronic Stability Control is one of many advanced safety features on this 2014 Ford Focus . The high efficiency automatic transmission shifts smoothly and allows you to relax while driving. Small and nimble this 2014 Ford Focus scoots through traffic. It offers great fuel mileage and ease of parking.

Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and convenience with this 2014 Nissan Versa Note SV. This compact hatchback is the ideal choice for the modern driver seeking a practical and well-equipped vehicle.

Featuring a vibrant Teal exterior, this Versa Note SV boasts an impressive array of desirable features:

- Cruise Control
- Backup Camera
- Bluetooth
- FLOOR & CARGO MATS (5-PIECE SET)
- SPLASH GUARDS

Beyond the standout amenities, this Versa Note delivers exceptional fuel economy, with an EPA-estimated 31 mpg in the city and 40 mpg on the highway. The 1.6L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, paired with a CVT with Xtronic transmission, ensures a smooth and efficient driving experience.

Slip behind the wheel and discover the comfort and convenience of this well-appointed Versa Note. The interior is thoughtfully designed, with features like air conditioning, power windows, and remote keyless entry, ensuring a pleasant driving experience. The Upgraded Cloth Seat Trim and Split folding rear seat provide both style and functionality, while the Steering wheel mounted audio controls and Tilt steering wheel allow you to stay connected and in control.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Versa Note SV boasting a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. Dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control work together to provide a secure and confident ride.

Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2014 Nissan Versa Note SV is the perfect companion. With its exceptional fuel efficiency, ample cargo space, and impressive array of features, this hatchback is sure to exceed your expectations.

Experience the joy of driving with this well-equipped and versatile 2014 Nissan Versa Note SV. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can enhance your daily commute and weekend adventures.

Discover the ultimate off-road companion in the 2023 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4X. This exceptional vehicle is designed to conquer any terrain, delivering unparalleled capability and refined luxury.

Elevating the off-road experience, the AT4X AEV Edition features:
• AEV front chassis skid plate
• AEV transfer case skid plate
• AEV stamped-steel rear bumper with heavy-duty cast recovery points
• 18" 12-spoke high-gloss black aluminum wheels with laser etching and AEV center cap
• AEV rear differential skid plate
• Rocker protection
• AEV branded floor liners
• AEV fuel tank skid plate
• Black gloss door handles
• AEV branded front head restraints and tailgate decal with exterior badging

The AT4X package also includes a Trailering Package, ensuring you can confidently tow your gear with ease.

Elevating your driving experience, this Sierra 1500 AT4X boasts an impressive array of premium features, including:
• Navigation system
• Bose premium series audio system with 12 speakers
• Heads-up display
• Remote vehicle starter
• Off-road suspension
• Power moonroof
• HD surround vision
• Heated steering wheel
• Lane keep assist with lane departure warning
• Wireless phone projection
• Heated and ventilated front seats

Certified as a one-owner vehicle with a clean CARFAX report, this 2023 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4X is the ultimate blend of capability, technology, and luxury. Experience the power and refinement that only the AT4X can deliver.

Imagine conquering the most challenging off-road trails with confidence, while enjoying the comfort and convenience of premium amenities. This Sierra 1500 AT4X is the perfect companion for your next adventure, whether it's exploring the great outdoors or tackling your daily commute.

At our dealership, we take pride in offering exceptional vehicles that exceed our customers' expectations. We invite you to experience the unparalleled capabilities and refined luxury of the 2023 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4X. Schedule a test drive today and discover the ultimate off-road experience.

Welcome to Findlay Toyota in Flagstaff. All of our vehicles are hand picked and reconditioned for your peace of mind. Each vehicle has been through an inspection and reconditioning process so that we can bring you the vehicles you really want to drive. We are pleased to offer this 2017 Chevrolet Spark 1LT and more at www.findlaytoyotaflagstaff.net

• Clean Carfax
• 6-Speaker Audio System Feature
• ABS brakes
• Dual front impact airbags
• Dual front side impact airbags
• Emergency communication system: OnStar
• Front anti-roll bar
• Front wheel independent suspension
• Knee airbag
• Low tire pressure warning
• Occupant sensing airbag
• Overhead airbag
• Power Emergency Unlock Automatic Door Locks
• Rear side impact airbag
• Remote Keyless Entry w/Panic Alarm Button
• Brake assist
• Electronic Stability Control
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• 15" x 6" Alloy Wheels

This 2017 Chevrolet Spark 1LT is a compact and efficient vehicle that delivers an impressive 30 city/38 highway MPG. Powered by a 1.4L DOHC engine and CVT transmission, this Spark provides a smooth and responsive driving experience. With its sleek gray exterior and well-appointed interior, this Spark is both stylish and practical.

The Spark 1LT comes equipped with a host of advanced features, including a 6-speaker audio system, Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, and a rearview camera. Safety is also a top priority, with features like OnStar emergency communication, dual front and side impact airbags, and electronic stability control.

Whether you're looking for a commuter car, a first-time vehicle, or a nimble city driver, this 2017 Chevrolet Spark 1LT is an excellent choice. With its combination of efficiency, technology, and safety features, it's a smart and practical option that won't break the bank. We invite you to come in and take this Spark for a test drive. Our team of knowledgeable sales professionals is here to answer any questions you may have and help you find the perfect vehicle to fit your lifestyle and budget.

description:
This 2017 Hyundai Elantra GT Base offers a compelling blend of style, efficiency, and versatility, making it an exceptional choice for the discerning driver. With its sleek silver exterior and well-appointed interior, this Elantra GT exudes a refined and modern aesthetic that is sure to turn heads.

• 2.0L DOHC engine with 6-Speed Automatic Transmission
• 24 city/32 highway MPG
• AM/FM/SiriusXM/CD/MP3 Audio System
• Air Conditioning
• Power Windows and Remote Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
• 4-Wheel Disc Brakes with ABS
• Dual Front and Side Impact Airbags
• Electronic Stability Control
• Rear Spoiler and Heated Power Door Mirrors

The Elantra GT's responsive handling and efficient powertrain deliver a driving experience that is both engaging and economical. With its spacious interior and versatile cargo area, this hatchback offers the perfect balance of practicality and performance, making it an ideal companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin featuring premium cloth seating surfaces and a host of convenient amenities. The split-folding rear seat allows you to easily accommodate larger items, while the standard air conditioning and rear defroster ensure your comfort in any weather.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Elantra GT boasting a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. Dual front and side impact airbags, 4-wheel disc brakes with ABS, and Electronic Stability Control work together to provide you and your passengers with a secure and confident driving experience.

Whether you're in the market for a practical daily driver or a versatile hatchback that can handle your active lifestyle, this 2017 Hyundai Elantra GT Base is an exceptional choice. We invite you to experience its impressive combination of style, efficiency, and technology by scheduling a test drive at our showroom today.

description: 2017 Toyota Prius One — Hypersonic Red exterior with Moonstone cloth interior. This vehicle is in excellent overall condition and is powered by Toyota’s Hybrid Synergy Drive system combining a 1.8L Atkinson-cycle inline-4 gasoline engine with an electric motor for a combined output of approximately 121 hp. EPA fuel-economy ratings are 54 MPG city and 50 MPG highway. Powertrain and driving features - 1.8L hybrid I-4 paired with an electric motor and a continuously variable transmission (CVT). - Regenerative braking system to recapture energy under braking. - Drive-mode selection including Normal, Eco and EV modes to optimize efficiency and responsiveness. - Conventional front-wheel drive layout. Exterior - Hypersonic Red factory paint. - Aerodynamic body design characteristic of the Prius to reduce wind resistance and improve fuel economy. - Projector-style halogen headlights with daytime running lights. - 15-inch steel wheels with full covers (factory standard wheel treatment). - Body-color exterior mirrors and door handles. - Rear liftgate with integrated spoiler for cargo access and improved aerodynamics. Interior and comfort - Moonstone cloth seating surfaces in a neutral light-tone finish. - Seating for five with a 60/40 split-folding rear seat to expand cargo capacity and versatility. - Automatic climate control with air filtration and vents positioned for front and rear occupant comfort. - Tilt/telescoping steering column. - Power windows and power door locks with remote keyless entry. - Multiple storage locations including center console bin, door pockets and cupholders. Convenience and technology - Touchscreen infotainment system (factory standard display) with AM/FM radio, USB and auxiliary inputs and Bluetooth connectivity for hands-free calling and audio streaming. - Steering-wheel mounted audio and phone controls. - Rearview backup camera for easier maneuvering and parking. - Trip computer and multi-information display with fuel economy readouts, hybrid system information and range estimation. Safety and driver assists - Comprehensive passive and active safety systems including front, side and curtain airbags and driver’s knee airbag. - Anti-lock Braking System (ABS), Electronic Brake-force Distribution (EBD) and brake assist. - Vehicle Stability Control and traction control to help maintain directional control. - Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS). - Factory-installed advanced driver assistance features included in Toyota’s safety package for the model year: forward collision mitigation, lane departure alert/assist, automatic high beams and adaptive cruise control (as part of the original factory safety suite). Cargo and utility - A practical cargo area accessed via the rear hatch with fold-flat rear seats for carrying larger items. - Low load floor for easier loading and everyday usability. This 2017 Prius One presents as a fuel-efficient, well-equipped compact hybrid with the factory standard features expected for the model year, finished in Hypersonic Red with Moonstone cloth, and noted to be in excellent overall condition. Buy worry-free! Our vehicles come with a 3000 mile / 3 Month Powertrain Warranty! This deal won't last! Call us today to schedule a test drive! **Exclusions may apply

description:
Adventure Subaru is proud to offer this 2017 Toyota Corolla iM in Electric Storm Blue, a compact hatchback that blends efficiency, reliability, and everyday comfort in a smart, approachable package. It has been thoroughly inspected, is ready to take home, and offers an easy driving experience that fits both commuting and weekend errands.

Inside, the Corolla iM feels well laid out and comfortable. Supportive front seats, dual-zone automatic climate control, and fabric upholstery create a cabin that is simple and practical without feeling bare. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob add a refined touch, while the versatile hatchback design and split-folding rear seat make it easy to adapt the space for groceries, gear, or longer trips.

Technology and convenience are thoughtfully integrated. The 7-inch Toyota iM Display Audio system keeps controls easy to reach, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls help you stay focused on the road. Features like keyless entry, a rear vision camera, and fully automatic headlights add confidence and ease to daily driving.

Safety and stability are core strengths of this Corolla iM. With electronic stability control, traction control, anti-lock brakes, and a full suite of airbags, it is designed to help you feel supported and secure. Four-wheel independent suspension and alloy wheels contribute to a ride that feels composed and comfortable over a variety of road surfaces.

This Corolla iM has been well maintained and delivers excellent fuel efficiency, rated at 28 city and 36 highway miles per gallon, making it an economical choice for everyday driving. It also earned recognition from Kelley Blue Book for both overall brand awards and resale value, reflecting Toyotas long-standing reputation for dependability.

At Adventure Subaru, we want your entire experience to feel convenient and stress-free. You can complete your purchase online or visit us in our eco-friendly dealership, and enjoy added value like complimentary car washes and courtesy transportation.

Come take a look at this vehicle at Adventure Subaru and Experience Where You Truly Belong.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Whether you're seeking a stylish and tech-savvy daily driver or a versatile companion for your active lifestyle, this 2015 Ford Focus Titanium is an exceptional choice. Schedule a test drive today and experience the exceptional value and performance this vehicle has to offer.

description: 2015 Mazda Mazda3 i Touring — Brown exterior, Black interior. Powered by Mazda’s SKYACTIV-G 2.0L I4 producing 155 hp and 150 lb-ft of torque, this Mazda3 delivers efficient, responsive performance and is rated at 29 MPG city / 40 MPG highway. The vehicle is in excellent overall condition and comes with a clean CARFAX report. Factory-equipped features (standard Touring-level equipment): - Powertrain and efficiency: SKYACTIV-G 2.0L engine with Mazda’s SKYACTIV engineering for improved fuel economy and drivability. - Transmission and driving aids: Mazda’s SKYACTIV transmission technology (factory drivetrain configuration) plus standard driver aids that enhance control and stability. - Safety systems: Anti-lock Braking System (ABS), Electronic Brakeforce Distribution (EBD), traction control and electronic stability control, front airbags, front-seat side-impact airbags and side curtain airbags, and a Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS). - Exterior features: Brown factory paint, compact aerodynamic body styling, halogen headlamps, integrated side mirrors, and factory alloy wheels. - Interior and comfort: Black cloth seating with supportive front seats and a 60/40 split-folding rear seat for added cargo versatility, manual climate controls, tilt-and-telescoping steering wheel, center armrest and practical storage compartments. - Convenience and controls: Power windows and door locks, remote keyless entry, cruise control, and steering-wheel-mounted audio and phone controls. - Infotainment and connectivity: Factory audio system with AM/FM and auxiliary/USB inputs, Bluetooth hands-free phone and audio streaming capability for phone integration and media playback. - Practical features: Split-folding rear seats to expand cargo capacity, multiple cupholders and cubby storage, and easy-to-use driver ergonomics typical of Mazda’s interior design. This Mazda3 i Touring offers a balanced mix of efficiency, everyday practicality and a well-equipped factory feature set in an attractive brown exterior with a black interior. Clean CARFAX and excellent overall condition make it a reliable choice for drivers seeking fuel-efficient transportation with a solid factory equipment list. description: The 2015 Toyota Prius is a remarkable hybrid hatchback that combines efficiency with practicality, making it an ideal choice for eco-conscious drivers. Featuring a striking Nautical Blue Metallic exterior and a comfortable Bisque interior, this used vehicle offers a stylish yet functional design. With only 141,808 miles on the odometer, it delivers reliable performance powered by a 1.8-liter four-cylinder engine paired with a seamless hybrid system. The Prius’s front-wheel drive and naturally aspirated setup produce 134 horsepower, ensuring smooth acceleration and excellent fuel economy—up to 51 mpg in the city and 48 mpg on the highway. Modern convenience features like Bluetooth connectivity, keyless entry, and push start make daily driving effortless, while its four-door layout comfortably seats five passengers, perfect for families or commuters seeking a practical, fuel-efficient vehicle. This 2015 Toyota Prius stands out with its combination of advanced safety and security features, designed to keep occupants protected on every journey. It includes driver-side knee airbags and active head restraints at the front, enhancing safety in the event of a collision. The regenerative braking system not only improves efficiency but also supports the vehicle’s braking performance, while four-wheel anti-lock brakes deliver confident stopping power. Auto-locking power door locks provide added security when the vehicle is parked, giving peace of mind to owners. These features, along with its reliable build and hybrid technology, make the Prius an excellent choice for those seeking a safe, secure, and environmentally friendly vehicle. 2015 Toyota Prius Safety and Security Features The safety features of this Prius prioritize driver and passenger protection, starting with knee airbags for the driver, which help mitigate injury in a frontal collision. The regenerative braking system enhances safety by recovering energy during deceleration, thereby improving overall braking efficiency. Active head restraints at the front provide additional protection against whiplash injuries, while four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) ensures stable stopping under various road conditions. Auto-locking power door locks add a layer of security, automatically locking doors when the vehicle is in motion to prevent unauthorized access and enhance safety during daily use. 2015 Toyota Prius Entertainment and Technology Features Entertainment and technology are well integrated in the 2015 Prius, offering drivers and passengers a seamless experience. An auxiliary audio input compatible with iPod and iPhone devices allows for easy music streaming and connectivity, keeping everyone entertained on the go. The vehicle’s infotainment system features a 6.1-inch display screen, providing clear access to audio, navigation, and vehicle information. These features combine to deliver a modern, user-friendly interface that enhances the driving experience while maintaining the Prius’s reputation for efficiency and innovation. 2015 Toyota Prius Performance Features Underneath its sleek exterior, the 2015 Toyota Prius is equipped with performance features that emphasize efficiency and reliability. The auto start/stop function automatically turns off the engine when the vehicle is stationary, conserving fuel and reducing emissions. Its electric motor utilizes a nickel-metal hydride battery, a proven and durable power source that supports the hybrid system’s seamless transition between gasoline and electric power. These technologies work together to provide a smooth, efficient ride while maintaining the Prius’s reputation as a leader in hybrid automotive innovation.

The power-adjustable seats with lumbar support ensure you stay comfortable on long drives, while the rear bench seat offers versatility for passengers or cargo. With performance tires and aluminum wheels, the Golf GTI not only looks the part but delivers on its promise of sporty agility. This hatchback is more than a car it s a statement of style and performance. Be sure to call or visit Town East Ford to discover more. description: Introducing the 2015 Ford Fiesta ST, a dynamic blend of thrilling performance, stylish design, and unbeatable value, ready to ignite your driving passion! This sporty hatchback, dressed in a striking blue exterior, commands attention with every curve and contour, exuding an aura of excitement and energy that’s impossible to resist. Under the hood, the Fiesta ST houses a spirited EcoBoost 1.6L Turbocharged I4 engine, delivering a robust 197 horsepower and 202 ft. lbs. of torque. This powerhouse of an engine ensures every drive is a pulse-quickening experience, perfectly paired with a 6-speed manual transmission that offers a hands-on, exhilarating connection to the road. Whether you're navigating city streets or carving through winding backroads, the Fiesta ST promises a responsive and engaging ride that leaves a lasting impression. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a sleek and functional interior adorned with black cloth seats that provide both comfort and style. The cabin is thoughtfully designed to enhance your driving experience, offering intuitive controls and modern conveniences that make every journey enjoyable. The Fiesta ST isn’t just about performance, it’s about creating a driving environment that’s as inviting as it is exciting. This 2015 Ford Fiesta ST isn’t just a car, it’s a statement of style and substance. It has earned its place among the best of the best, as recognized by multiple prestigious awards. It's a proud recipient of Edmunds's Top 10 Least Expensive Hatchbacks and Wagons and Top Recommended Performance and Sports Cars, showcasing its exceptional value and thrilling performance. Additionally, it has been lauded in the J.D. Power and Associates's Automotive Performance, Execution and Layout (APEAL) Study as a top model in its segment, underscoring its superior design and execution. Not to mention, it’s been named one of Kelley Blue Book's 10 Coolest Cars Under $18k and $25k, proving that it’s not just about affordability, but about delivering an unmatched cool factor. With 116,006 miles on the odometer, this Fiesta ST has been well-loved, yet it stands ready to deliver many more miles of joy and adventure. It’s a testament to Ford’s commitment to durability and performance, ensuring that you can drive with confidence, knowing that this vehicle has been engineered to last. In the world of compact sports cars, the 2015 Ford Fiesta ST stands out as a true champion. Its combination of performance, style, and value is unparalleled, making it an ideal choice for those who refuse to compromise on driving excitement. This is not just a car, it’s a lifestyle choice for those who crave the thrill of the drive and the freedom of the open road. Don’t miss the opportunity to own this award-winning hatchback. The 2015 Ford Fiesta ST is more than just a vehicle, it’s an experience waiting to be had. Visit us today and take the Fiesta ST for a test drive. Feel the power, embrace the style, and discover why this car continues to capture hearts and minds worldwide. Your next adventure awaits!

Thank you for choosing Chapman Ford Lancaster, this Meteor Gray Mica 2015 Mazda Mazda3 s Touring is a great choice! Check out the following: City 26/Hwy 35 METEOR GRAY MICA, BLACK, LEATHERETTE SEAT TRIM, LEV EMISSIONS EQUIPMENT, WHEEL LOCKS Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Head-up display - Keep your head up! You don't have to take your eyes off of the road to get information from your dashboard anymore. With head-up display, important driving information - like speed and RPM's - displays on your windshield in your line of sight. Because when you're driving, the most important information lies on the road ahead. Keep your eyes on the road with head-up display.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.
